{"tid":926002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢夢到，芝麻社會信用已經應用響港澳人身上","createTime":"2018-12-03T06:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T08:25:13.000Z","uid":64191,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3135882930f948ab8d666b248017866d8b1a6c01","tid":926002,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:37:58.000Z","msg":"近年大家都聽過咩叫「芝麻信用」、「社會信用」啦，中國更於部分地區試用「社會信用」系統，將來擴散到全國。港澳人聞訊後卻反應冷淡，以為一國兩制下未必應用諸彼<br />\n<br />\n我最近發左個怪夢，夢見幾個熱愛到中國消遣既港澳朋友，近日因爲「芝麻信用不足」為由，拒絕其預約酒店及購買火車飛，本身佢地早就預約妥當，但對方以「政府命令，兩岸關係緊張，不接待外賓」為由，拒絕受理港澳客人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個夢認真奇怪，港澳人唔係中國既一份子嗎？照理應該一個都不能少，我響夢境中求證友人既信用評分，佢地並無走數、失言紀錄，仲好愛國添！但初始分數卻係低到慘不忍睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡直奇怪，莫非港澳人初始分數就係「低信用」？夢境太奇怪，怪到我就此醒來了⋯"},{"pid":"dab78602cc9427a3cf1c3f39eb40e0c25562e40f","tid":926002,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:39:29.000Z","msg":"在下墾求各位解夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6618a122674dd32d473f706cd35dac99f34ab3","tid":926002,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb642e6be191921f39be34f101f9b1db4f2ecc9","tid":926002,"uid":52943,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:03:21.000Z","msg":"你好著緊個芝麻信用評分? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚無得返上去享受祖國榮耀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7005563b9c171db5cd8b6b75b409b19b04d81c41","tid":926002,"uid":43575,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"死番大陸啦"},{"pid":"e2ddd917f3b2d08f6abb7c8a2b3d4531a03c0a8e","